  "text": "We next studied a collection of 13 pediatric cancer cases that we sequenced-both tumor and normalusing 10X Genomics Chromium WGS and Whole-Exome Sequencing (WES). One of these cases was studied previously [CITATION_1] , and the other twelve are novel to this work. We ran Samovar, MosaicHunter (in both paired and tumor-only modes), and MuTect2 (in both paired and tumor-only modes) on each of the 13 tumor WGS datasets. When running MosaicHunter or MuTect2 in paired mode, we also provided the paired normal WGS.",
